  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The sum of a number <math alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi>\n</math> and <math alttext=\"7\"><mn>7</mn>\n</math> is twice as large as a number <math alttext=\"y\"><mi>y</mi>\n</math>. The number <math alttext=\"y\"><mi>y</mi>\n</math> is <math alttext=\"3\"><mn>3</mn>\n</math> less than the number <math alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi>\n</math>. Which system of equations describes this situation?</p>",
